- develop your hospitality skills and put them into practice 
- help us raise funds towards saving nature 

Food Hygiene Level 2 and Allergen Awareness training is mandatory for all working in the café.   

You’ll be provided with the necessary induction, training, and equipment do this role well and safely, and we can cover the travel costs between home and your place of volunteering.  

You can choose which shifts to do to fit round your other commitments.""";
