                            :description """Grimsby Community Energy (GCE) is seeking a volunteer solicitor to support our renewable energy projects by helping us finalise and manage legal agreements with host sites. This role is ideal for a qualified or recently retired solicitor with experience in commercial property or energy law, who wants to use their expertise to benefit a local, community-owned energy enterprise.
