                            :description """Maintaining Flatford Wildlife Garden in the best condition for wildlife and to inspire visitors to make their own gardens welcoming to nature takes a lot of effort and many hands. We’re looking for someone to join the Thursday work party team at Flatford Wildlife Garden to help keep on top of basic garden maintenance tasks.

